<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>{{ project_title }} — {{ subtitle }}</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f5f6f8;
    --panel: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1f2933;
    --muted: #5c6773;
    --line: #e3e6ea;
    --accent: #1f4f8b;
    --accent-soft: #e8f0f9;
    --high: #b3261e;
    --high-soft: #fdecea;
    --medium: #b06b00;
    --medium-soft: #fff4d6;
    --low: #2f6f4d;
    --low-soft: #e6f4ec;
    --positive: #2f6f4d;
    --negative: #b3261e;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB",
      "Helvetica Neue", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .page {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 28px 64px;
  }
  header.hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f4f8b 0%, #2f6f8f 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(31, 79, 139, 0.18);
  }
  header.hero .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  header.hero h1 {
    margin: 6px 0 4px;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  header.hero .subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  header.hero .positioning {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  header.hero .positioning .lang-en {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  header.hero .positioning .lang-cn {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 6px;
    opacity: 0.88;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  header.hero .meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.92;
  }
  header.hero .meta span strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 18px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-left: 3px solid #ffd66b;
  }
  .disclaimer .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #ffd66b;
    color: #5b3b00;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  section.panel {
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  section.panel > h2 {
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  section.panel > .section-hint {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .stat-card .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .stat-card .value {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .stat-card.tone-high { background: var(--high-soft); border-color: #f3c2bd; }
  .stat-card.tone-high .value { color: var(--high); }
  .stat-card.tone-medium { background: var(--medium-soft); border-color: #f0d79a; }
  .stat-card.tone-medium .value { color: var(--medium); }
  .stat-card.tone-low { background: var(--low-soft); border-color: #b9dac5; }
  .stat-card.tone-low .value { color: var(--low); }
  .meta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 14px;
  }
  .meta-row strong { color: var(--ink); }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  table th, table td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  table th {
    background: #f7f9fb;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .severity-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .severity-pill.high { background: var(--high-soft); color: var(--high); }
  .severity-pill.medium { background: var(--medium-soft); color: var(--medium); }
  .severity-pill.low { background: var(--low-soft); color: var(--low); }
  .delta-positive { color: var(--positive); font-weight: 600; }
  .delta-negative { color: var(--negative); font-weight: 600; }
  .delta-neutral { color: var(--muted); }
  .target-block {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    border: 1px solid #c4d6ed;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .target-block h3 {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .target-block .target-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .target-block .target-meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .driver-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-rank {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-role {
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-contribution {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .driver-card .driver-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .driver-card .driver-meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .driver-card p { margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .process-group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .process-group h3 {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .roadmap {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .roadmap .card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .roadmap .card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .roadmap ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .roadmap li { margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .limitations-list { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .limitations-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .limitations-list .source {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .next-steps-list { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  .next-steps-list li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .next-steps-list .source-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  footer.footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .empty {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .exec-summary {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f3f7fc 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    border: 1px solid #c4d6ed;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .exec-summary h2 {
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .exec-summary .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .exec-summary ol {
    margin: 10px 0 0;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .exec-summary li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .exec-summary li::marker {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .glossary {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: #fafbfc;
    border: 1px dashed var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .glossary .item {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .glossary .item strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .glossary .divider {
    color: var(--line);
    user-select: none;
  }
  .soft-table th {
    background: #fbfcfd;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .soft-table tr:hover td { background: #f7faff; }
  .soft-table .severity-pill {
    background: #f3f5f7;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .soft-table .severity-pill.high {
    background: #fff2ef;
    color: #8b2c20;
    border-color: #f3c2bd;
  }
  .soft-table .severity-pill.medium {
    background: #fff8e0;
    color: #7a4a00;
    border-color: #f0d79a;
  }
  .contribution-bar {
    height: 8px;
    width: 100%;
    background: #eef2f7;
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .contribution-bar > .fill {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1f4f8b 0%, #4a8fcf 100%);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .driver-card .contribution-wrap {
    flex: 1 1 220px;
    min-width: 200px;
  }
  .driver-card .contribution-wrap .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .driver-card .role-explanation {
    margin: 6px 0 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: #f6f8fb;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-soft);
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .evidence-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .evidence-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fafbfc;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-negative {
    background: var(--high-soft);
    border-color: #f3c2bd;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-positive {
    background: var(--low-soft);
    border-color: #b9dac5;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-neutral {
    background: #f7f9fb;
    border-color: var(--line);
  }
  .evidence-card .chain-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .evidence-card .tone-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-negative .tone-tag {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--high);
    border: 1px solid #f3c2bd;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-positive .tone-tag {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--low);
    border: 1px solid #b9dac5;
  }
  .evidence-card.tone-neutral .tone-tag {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .evidence-card .headline {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .evidence-detail {
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .evidence-detail summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    list-style: none;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #fbfcfd;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .evidence-detail summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .evidence-detail[open] summary { background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent); }
  .evidence-detail table { margin-top: 10px; }
  .portfolio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .portfolio-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #fff;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .portfolio-card .eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .portfolio-card .title {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .portfolio-card .stat {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .portfolio-card .desc-en {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .portfolio-card .desc-cn {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .fusion-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .fusion-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .fusion-card .layer {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .fusion-card .role {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .fusion-card .detail-en {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 6px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .fusion-card .detail-cn {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .fusion-boundary {
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: #fff8e0;
    border-left: 3px solid #e0b94a;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: #5b3b00;
  }
  .jargon-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .jargon-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .jargon-card .term {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .jargon-card .plain {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .jargon-card .plain-cn {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 2px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .roi-summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .roi-stat {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .roi-stat .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .roi-stat .value {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .roi-stat .hint {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .demo-only-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #fff;
    color: #7a4a00;
    border: 1px solid #e0b94a;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-left: 6px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main class="page">

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">{{ dashboard_version }}</div>
    <h1>{{ project_title }}</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">{{ subtitle }}</div>
    <div class="positioning" role="note" aria-label="project positioning">
      <span class="lang-en">{{ project_positioning_en }}</span>
      <span class="lang-cn">{{ project_positioning_cn }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta">
      <span><strong>报告生成时间</strong>：{{ generated_at_display }}</span>
      {% if overview.baseline_window %}
      <span><strong>基线窗口</strong>：{{ overview.baseline_window }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if overview.recent_window %}
      <span><strong>最近窗口</strong>：{{ overview.recent_window }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if report_version %}
      <span><strong>M3 报告版本</strong>：{{ report_version }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      <span class="tag">Demo Disclaimer</span>
      {{ demo_disclaimer }}
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="panel" id="portfolio">
    <h2>Portfolio at a glance · 30 秒看懂这份 Dashboard</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">
      为没有消费金融背景的访客准备的一屏式导览：业务问题 → 数据底座 → 异常 → 归因 → 策略 ROI。所有数字均来自 synthetic data。
    </div>
    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      {% for card in portfolio_cards %}
      <div class="portfolio-card" data-portfolio-card="{{ card.code }}">
        <div class="eyebrow">{{ card.eyebrow }}</div>
        <div class="title">{{ card.title }}</div>
        <div class="stat">{{ card.stat }}</div>
        <div class="desc-en">{{ card.description_en }}</div>
        <div class="desc-cn">{{ card.description_cn }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="ai-ml-fusion">
    <h2>AI + ML Fusion · 各层职责</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">
      本 demo 不把 LLM 当作自动金融决策者；ML / 规则、归因 / ROI、LLM / Agent 各自负责不同环节，关键动作必须由人复核。
    </div>
    <div class="fusion-grid">
      {% for layer in ai_ml_fusion_layers %}
      <div class="fusion-card">
        <div class="layer">{{ layer.layer }}</div>
        <div class="role">{{ layer.role }}</div>
        <div class="detail-en">{{ layer.detail_en }}</div>
        <div class="detail-cn">{{ layer.detail_cn }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="fusion-boundary">
      <strong>Human-in-the-loop boundary</strong>：LLM is not used as an automatic financial decision maker. Every action requires explicit human approval; no SMS / voice / WhatsApp is sent; no real customer is contacted.
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="jargon">
    <h2>Jargon glossary · 一眼读懂术语</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">
      下列术语会反复出现在异常 / 归因 / 过程证据 / ROI 模块中，先看一眼避免迷失。
    </div>
    <div class="jargon-grid">
      {% for entry in jargon_glossary %}
      <div class="jargon-card">
        <div class="term">{{ entry.term }}</div>
        <div class="plain">{{ entry.plain }}</div>
        <div class="plain-cn">{{ entry.cn }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="overview">
    <h2>1. 异常总览</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">基于 M3-A 异常检测引擎输出，统计本轮触发的异常数量与严重度分布。</div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for card in overview.cards %}
      <div class="stat-card tone-{{ card.tone }}">
        <div class="label">{{ card.label }}</div>
        <div class="value">{{ card.value }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span><strong>归因目标指标</strong>：{{ attribution_target.metric_name_cn }}（{{ attribution_target.metric_code }}）</span>
      {% if attribution_target.anomaly_id %}
      <span><strong>归因目标 anomaly_id</strong>：{{ attribution_target.anomaly_id }}</span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if overview.warnings %}
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span><strong>warnings</strong>：{{ overview.warnings | join('；') }}</span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="exec-summary" id="exec-summary">
    <div class="eyebrow">Executive Summary</div>
    <h2>本期一句话结论</h2>
    {% if executive_summary %}
    <ol>
      {% for line in executive_summary %}
      <li>{{ line }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">本轮未生成结论。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="high-priority">
    <h2>2. 高优先级异常列表</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">按 severity 排序展示需要优先处置的异常事件；表格已做视觉减压，仅在 severity / 相对变化两列保留弱色提醒。</div>
    {% if high_priority_anomalies %}
    <table class="soft-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>指标</th>
          <th>严重度<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">severity</span></th>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>历史基准<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">baseline</span></th>
          <th>最近窗口<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">recent</span></th>
          <th>相对变化<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">relative change</span></th>
          <th>下一步建议</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for anomaly in high_priority_anomalies %}
        <tr>
          <td>
            <strong>{{ anomaly.metric_name_cn or anomaly.metric_code }}</strong><br/>
            <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px;">{{ anomaly.metric_code }}</span>
          </td>
          <td>
            <span class="severity-pill {{ anomaly.severity }}">{{ anomaly.severity }}</span>
          </td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.dimension_name }} = {{ anomaly.dimension_value }}</td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
          <td>
            {% set rc = anomaly.relative_change %}
            {% if rc is number %}
              {% if rc > 0 %}
              <span class="delta-positive">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% elif rc < 0 %}
              <span class="delta-negative">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% else %}
              <span class="delta-neutral">{{ rc | signed_pct }}</span>
              {% endif %}
            {% else %}
              N/A
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>{{ anomaly.recommended_next_step or '—' }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="glossary" aria-label="字段说明">
      <span class="item"><strong>字段说明</strong></span>
      {% for entry in high_priority_glossary %}
      <span class="divider">·</span>
      <span class="item"><strong>{{ entry.cn }}</strong> = {{ entry.en }}（{{ entry.hint }}）</span>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">本轮无 high severity 异常。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="attribution">
    <h2>3. M1 D7 回收率下降归因</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">基于 M3-B 归因引擎对目标指标 {{ attribution_target.metric_code }} 的 Top drivers 进行解读。</div>

    {% if attribution_target.anomaly %}
    {% set tgt = attribution_target.anomaly %}
    <div class="target-block">
      <h3>归因目标异常：{{ tgt.metric_name_cn or tgt.metric_code }}</h3>
      <div class="target-meta">
        <span><strong>severity</strong>：<span class="severity-pill {{ tgt.severity }}">{{ tgt.severity }}</span></span>
        <span><strong>维度</strong>：{{ tgt.dimension_name }} = {{ tgt.dimension_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>baseline</strong>：{{ tgt.baseline_value | metric_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>recent</strong>：{{ tgt.recent_value | metric_value }}</span>
        <span><strong>relative change</strong>：
          {% if tgt.relative_change is number %}
            <span class="{% if tgt.relative_change > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif tgt.relative_change < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ tgt.relative_change | signed_pct }}</span>
          {% else %}
            N/A
          {% endif %}
        </span>
      </div>
      {% if tgt.explanation %}
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">{{ tgt.explanation }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <h3 style="margin: 12px 0 8px; font-size: 15px;">Top 5 drivers</h3>
    <div class="section-hint" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">贡献度横向条形图按当前 Top driver 最大值归一化，仅用于相对排序参考。</div>
    {% if top_drivers %}
      {% for driver in top_drivers %}
      <div class="driver-card">
        <div class="driver-head">
          <div>
            <span class="driver-rank">#{{ driver.rank }}</span>
            <span class="driver-title">{{ driver.dimension_name }} = {{ driver.dimension_value }}</span>
            <span class="driver-role">{{ driver.driver_role }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="contribution-wrap">
            <div class="label">贡献度 contribution</div>
            <div class="driver-contribution">{{ driver.contribution_score | pct }}</div>
            <div class="contribution-bar" aria-label="贡献度进度条">
              <span class="fill" style="width: {{ '%.1f' | format(driver.progress_pct) }}%;"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="driver-meta">
          <span><strong>历史基准</strong>：{{ driver.baseline_value | metric_value }}</span>
          <span><strong>最近窗口</strong>：{{ driver.recent_value | metric_value }}</span>
          {% if driver.confidence %}
          <span><strong>confidence</strong>：{{ driver.confidence }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if driver.role_explanation %}
        <p class="role-explanation"><strong>维度解读</strong>：{{ driver.role_explanation }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if driver.business_interpretation %}
        <p><strong>业务解释</strong>：{{ driver.business_interpretation }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if driver.recommended_action %}
        <p><strong>推荐动作</strong>：{{ driver.recommended_action }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">未生成 Top drivers。</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="process-evidence">
    <h2>4. Process evidence / driver linkage</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">先看证据链摘要卡片，再下钻明细表；分别覆盖触达、履约、策略工具、合规以及产能压力。</div>

    <div class="evidence-grid">
      {% for chain in evidence_chains %}
      <div class="evidence-card tone-{{ chain.tone }}">
        <div class="chain-label">
          <span>{{ chain.chain_label }}</span>
          <span class="tone-tag">{{ chain.tone_label }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="headline">{{ chain.headline }}</div>
        {% if chain.metric_focus %}
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted);">主指标：{{ chain.metric_focus }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <details class="evidence-detail">
      <summary>展开过程指标明细表（按 PTP / AI 外呼 / 减免 / 投诉 / 产能分组）</summary>

      {% for group in process_evidence_groups %}
      <div class="process-group">
        <h3>{{ group.group_label }}</h3>
        {% if group.entries %}
        <table class="soft-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>driver</th>
              <th>过程指标</th>
              <th>历史基准<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">baseline</span></th>
              <th>最近窗口<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">recent</span></th>
              <th>变化<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">delta</span></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for entry in group.entries %}
            <tr>
              <td>{{ entry.driver }}</td>
              <td>{{ entry.metric_name_cn or entry.metric_code }}</td>
              <td>{{ entry.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
              <td>{{ entry.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
              <td>
                {% if entry.delta is number %}
                  <span class="{% if entry.delta > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif entry.delta < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ entry.delta | signed_value }}</span>
                {% else %}
                  N/A
                {% endif %}
              </td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
        {% else %}
        <p class="empty">本轮 driver linkage 中未捕获该过程指标。</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

      <div class="process-group">
        <h3>产能压力信号</h3>
        {% if capacity_signals %}
        <table class="soft-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>指标</th>
              <th>维度</th>
              <th>历史基准<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">baseline</span></th>
              <th>最近窗口<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">recent</span></th>
              <th>相对变化<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">relative change</span></th>
              <th>说明</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for item in capacity_signals %}
            <tr>
              <td><strong>{{ item.metric_name_cn or item.metric_code }}</strong></td>
              <td>{{ item.dimension_name }} = {{ item.dimension_value }}</td>
              <td>{{ item.baseline_value | metric_value }}</td>
              <td>{{ item.recent_value | metric_value }}</td>
              <td>
                {% if item.relative_change is number %}
                  <span class="{% if item.relative_change > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif item.relative_change < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ item.relative_change | signed_pct }}</span>
                {% else %}
                  N/A
                {% endif %}
              </td>
              <td>{{ item.explanation or '—' }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
        {% else %}
        <p class="empty">本轮未捕获产能维度异常。</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </details>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="strategy-roi-lab">
    <h2>5. Strategy / ROI Lab <span class="demo-only-tag">demo assumptions only</span></h2>
    <div class="section-hint">
      离线策略情景估算：基于显式 demo 成本假设给出 delta / cost / net benefit / ROI / payback，仅用于演示，不代表真实财务结果，也不会触发任何真实催收动作。
    </div>
    {% if roi_block and roi_block.scenarios %}
    <div class="roi-summary-grid">
      <div class="roi-stat">
        <div class="label">Scenarios evaluated</div>
        <div class="value">{{ roi_block.scenario_count }}</div>
        <div class="hint">positive ROI: {{ roi_block.positive_roi_count }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="roi-stat">
        <div class="label">Top scenario</div>
        <div class="value">{{ roi_block.top_scenario_name or 'N/A' }}</div>
        <div class="hint">ROI {{ roi_block.top_roi_display }}</div>
      </div>
      {% if roi_block.cost_assumptions %}
      <div class="roi-stat">
        <div class="label">Assumed case base</div>
        <div class="value">{{ roi_block.cost_assumptions.assumed_case_base or 'N/A' }}</div>
        <div class="hint">unit recovery value: {{ roi_block.cost_assumptions.unit_recovery_value or 'N/A' }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="roi-stat">
        <div class="label">Payback window</div>
        <div class="value">{{ roi_block.cost_assumptions.payback_window_days or 'N/A' }} days</div>
        <div class="hint">demo assumption</div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <table class="soft-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Scenario</th>
          <th>Strategy type</th>
          <th>Δ on D7 recovery<br/><span style="font-weight: 400;">estimated delta</span></th>
          <th>Net benefit</th>
          <th>ROI</th>
          <th>Payback (days)</th>
          <th>Cost assumption</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for sc in roi_block.scenarios %}
        <tr>
          <td><strong>{{ sc.scenario_name or sc.scenario_id }}</strong></td>
          <td>{{ sc.strategy_type or '—' }}</td>
          <td>
            {% if sc.estimated_delta is number %}
            <span class="{% if sc.estimated_delta > 0 %}delta-positive{% elif sc.estimated_delta < 0 %}delta-negative{% else %}delta-neutral{% endif %}">{{ sc.estimated_delta_display }}</span>
            {% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>
            {% if sc.net_benefit is number %}
            {{ '%s' | format(sc.net_benefit) }}
            {% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>{{ sc.roi_ratio_display }}</td>
          <td>
            {% if sc.payback_period_days is number %}{{ '%.1f' | format(sc.payback_period_days) }}{% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
          <td style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px;">{{ sc.cost_assumption or '—' }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    {% if roi_block.demo_disclaimer %}
    <p style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic;">
      {{ roi_block.demo_disclaimer }}
    </p>
    {% endif %}
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">
      未检测到 ROI 输出（outputs/model_lab/roi_results.json）。可运行 <code>python scripts/riskops_cli.py render-model-lab</code> 重新生成。
      本 Demo 中所有 ROI 结果仅来自 demo cost assumptions，<strong>不代表真实财务结论</strong>。
    </p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="limitations">
    <h2>6. 数据局限与合规说明</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">Demo 环境使用的合成数据与隐私边界约束。</div>
    <ul class="limitations-list">
      {% for item in data_limitations %}
      <li>
        <span class="source">{{ item.source }}</span>{{ item.description }}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
      <li><span class="source">privacy</span>未接入真实客户数据，未触达真实客户，未发送短信 / 外呼，未涉及 P4 明文 PII 字段。</li>
      <li><span class="source">human_in_loop</span>所有结论均需人工复核，AI 不直接外发、不直接外呼、不绕过审批。</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" id="next-steps">
    <h2>7. 下一步建议</h2>
    <div class="section-hint">本轮异常与归因驱动的可执行建议（来自 M3-C 报告）。</div>
    {% if next_steps %}
    <ul class="next-steps-list">
      {% for item in next_steps %}
      <li>
        <span class="source-tag">{{ item.source }}</span>{{ item.next_step }}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% else %}
    <p class="empty">本轮未输出下一步建议。</p>
    {% endif %}

    <h3 style="margin: 18px 0 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted);">后续里程碑路线图</h3>
    <div class="roadmap">
      {% for phase in roadmap %}
      <div class="card">
        <h3>{{ phase.phase }}</h3>
        <ul>
          {% for item in phase.bullets %}
          <li>{{ item }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    RiskOps Copilot · {{ subtitle }} · 本页面基于合成数据，仅供 Demo 与作品集展示。
  </footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
